Description:
Description:
For the purpose of careful and efficient provision of information to all parties involved in the forced departure (expulsion) of a foreign national(Vreemdeling), the registration form, model MBES18, is required.

Solution:
Create a new module in Tab Opsporing called MBES18.
When opening this module a grid wil show as in Arrestanten, with the Options volgnummer, Datum incident, Bijzonderheden, Organisatie, Contact persoon, telefoon numer, Voornaam, Achternaam en Geboortedatum.

Testplan:
Step 1: Go to Opsporing and choose tab MBES18
Step 2: Grid as attachment should pop up
Step 3: Grid should contain columns mentioned.

Navigation:
Opsporing - MBES18

Description:
Per incident a new record should be created.
This should contain tab registratie, Personalia, Inbewaringstellings c.q. Plaatsingegevens, Gedrag/Medisch, Incidenten, Overige gegevens, Bezittingen/Bagage, Documenten.
In other task we will cover the various tabs. This task contains the registratie tab.

Solution:
Create the record for MBES18 records.
This should contain tab registratie, Personalia, Inbewaringstellings c.q. Plaatsingegevens, Gedrag/Medisch, Incidenten, Overige gegevens, Bezittingen/Bagage, Documenten.
In other task we will cover the various tabs. This task contains the registratie tab.

Testplan:
Step 1: Go to Opsporing - MBES18
Step 2: Enter all field in tab Registratie
Step 3: Save record

Navigation:
Opsporing - MBES18
